## How to Trigger Each Simulation

| # | Feature | Trigger |
|---|---------|---------|
| 1 | 🖥️ Attack Terminal | Attack Simulation → **Launch Attack** |
| 2 | 🧠 GAN Training | Traffic Generation → **Retrain Model** |
| 3 | 🎯 Training Exercise | Dashboard → **New Exercise** |
| 4 | 📡 Packet Inspector | Traffic Generation → **Generate** |
| 5 | 🗺️ Attack Map | Scenarios → any **Launch** button |

